N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 441.246 - Payor

State Regulations
A person or organization which pays the hospital for
services rendered to patients. This can be the patient and/or third party, such
as Medicare, Medicaid, Blue Cross or other private insurance
plan. Notes
